name: THE B-TEAM
summary: The alien invasion is underway! The best and the brightest met the enemy head on, and got their butts kicked for the trouble. Now it is up to you and the members of the B-Team! Dodge to the left. Dodge to the right. Dodge to the left. No, that’s your right. Speed down the path while dodging obstacles and overcoming deadly enemy traps! These aliens are carrying heavy firepower. Use the Team’s special weapons to fight through wave after wave of determined enemies. We are facing an enemy that is truly...
